jalse.entities

Class DefaultEntityContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • jalse.entities.DefaultEntityContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityContainer

    public class DefaultEntityContainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements EntityContainer
    An DefaultEntityContainer is a thread-safe implementation of EntityContainer.

    DefaultEntityContainer can take a delegate container to supply to EntityEvent. Entity updates will trigger these events using EntityListener.

    By default DefaultEntityContainer will use DefaultEntityFactory with no delegate container.
    Author:
    Elliot Ford
